{"tid":2051350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個對佢唔住嘅人","createTime":"2020-06-04T17:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T06:23:26.000Z","uid":345904,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb210531c502b601b5d1247d340861081ce467a","tid":2051350,"uid":345904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"唔限角度<br />\n屋企人 男女朋友 同學 朋友 老師 老細<br />\n乜都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係一個讀書唔叻 好易放棄嘅人<br />\n郁啲就頹到落底<br />\n但身邊出現咗一個對我好好嘅老師<br />\n鼓勵我支持我   幫我溫書   話對我有期望<br />\n最終都係入唔到U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過成績有進步<br />\n絕對唔係因為入唔到大學唔開心<br />\n只係覺得辜負咗佢對我嘅期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好對唔住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知咁多位巴絲有咩想分享吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99337149dc019116ddaf8cca0aeeed082af4b3b3","tid":2051350,"uid":326758,"like":85,"dislike":3,"score":82,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c058102475dcaa4543633df9756e58859ddf01","tid":2051350,"uid":136936,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:15:25.000Z","msg":"想當年中學上堂喺櫃桶玩電話，俾個巡樓嘅老師見到<br />\n為咗唔想記缺點，我屈9佢老花睇錯 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb65c0f228289b43cf8971d3c781ef1728e5cd63","tid":2051350,"uid":345904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"99337149dc019116ddaf8cca0aeeed082af4b3b3","tid":2051350,"uid":326758,"like":85,"dislike":3,"score":82,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:10:21.000Z","msg":"<